title: HDE Mini DisplayPort to VGA Female Adapter for MacTM
description: The HDE Mini DisplayPort to VGA adapter gives you the ability to connect your Mac computer to any video display that has VGA connection.  Simply plug the DisplayPort end into your device, and attach one end of a male/male VGA cable to the HDE Mini DisplayPort adapter, and the other to the VGA compatible Monitor, LCD Display, or projector for a clean and clear additional display!Compatible Devices:MacBook (Mid 2010) and later, MacBook Air (Late 2010) and later, MacBook Pro (Mid 2010) and later, Mac mini (Mid 2010) and later, iMac (Late 2009) and later, Mac Pro (Mid 2010), Windows Surface Tablets (2012), and Lenovo ThinkPad X1Notes*Adapter only works with tablets/laptops with Mini DisplayPort, please check with your device's output specification before placing order.*VGA does not support audio transmission
